reviews.content:
Multi side and side by side dont work.
Quick actions dont work.
Only thing that works is changing type of switcher, linear and grid.
Complete waste of money.
Screen gets cut off heavily in landscape mode on 2020 iPad Pro; would not recommend without PowerSelector for a quick respring. Otherwise you’re stuck with a cut off iPad.
The control centre buttons and other functions like side bar or something doesnt work. Only thing that works is prevent currently playing app from closing
Can confirm working fine on A12 ios 13.3

Works perfectly on my iPhone 11 Max Pro 
iOS 13.1.2 
Unc0ver 4.2.1
The ideia is amazing, but it just doesn’t work.
